OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice footage shows the arrest of
OL,4,C'prolific shoplifter' from Sheerness
OL,6,FA 'prolific' shoplifter who targeted
OL,7,Fshops on the Isle of Sheppey has been
OL,8,Fjailed for 18 months.
OL,10,FJosh Kennedy, from Sheerness, was
OL,11,Farrested on 19 February 2026 after he
OL,12,Fwas stopped by officers once he left a
OL,13,Fstore in Millenium Way with a basket
OL,14,Ffull of goods.
OL,16,FOfficers stopped the 31-year-old in
OL,17,FHope Street and found chocolate and
OL,18,Fcleaning products within his jacket.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
