CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice footage shows the arrest of
OL,4,C'prolific shoplifter' from Sheerness
OL,6,FFollowing further enquiries, officers
OL,7,Fcharged him with a further nine theft
OL,8,Foffences.
OL,10,FHe was found responsible for the theft
OL,11,Fof more than #775 worth of goods,
OL,12,Fincluding healthcare products and
OL,13,Fgroceries.
OL,15,FHe appeared at Medway Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt on 21 February 2026, where he
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty and was immediately
OL,18,Fsentenced to 18 months in custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
