PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice footage shows the arrest of
OL,4,C'prolific shoplifter' from Sheerness
OL,6,FInvestigating officer Police Constable
OL,7,FBethan Isaacs said: "Shoplifting
OL,8,Fcauses harm beyond the retailers
OL,9,Ftargeted, often leading to higher
OL,10,Fprices for local residents so
OL,11,Fbusinesses can offset their loses.
OL,13,F"Kent Police is firmly committed to
OL,14,Faddressing this behaviour, and I
OL,15,Fwelcome the custodial sentence imposed
OL,16,Fon Kennedy, which reflects the
OL,17,Fseriousness of his actions."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
